    "created_at": "2015-03-29T23:58:22Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-03-29T23:58:22Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "> Remove the call to register_events on the entire toolbar.\n\nThis means that elements in the toolbar can be focused (e.g. cell type select), where keyboard actions make sense, but will actually be triggering shortcuts. We added the call because this behavior was confusing.\n\n@ellisonbg I've opened #8191 with the first two of your bullets. Can you test that one out, and identify specifically what problems remain that we should fix for 3.1?\n"
  },
